RBD:
Iterate through all rbd's and get snapshots
 - take snapshot if latest snapshot is older than 24 hours
 - remove snapshots older than 7 days

CephFS:
- Daily incremental rsync
- Prune directories older than 7 days


Expose some metrics/status for monitoring


To use snapshot:

  rbd snap protect image@snap
  rbd clone image@snap newimagename --image-feature layering
  rbd map newimagename

